Remarks/Remarques: Curve created using open water measurements from 2021-2022 along with measurements above 30cms from 2018 onward. These measurements were trending to the right of the previous rating.The record high measurement indivertibly plots on this rating- this was unintentional as there appears to be a control change between 2012 and 2017. The upper estimated range is applied based on the high measurement from 2017-06-17, not the record high from 2007. No grade is applied to the lower range, based on the low measurement from 2023-01-26.
Minor Change in Zero flow point at 2012 second peak, Extended top end
